<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Welcome to AgriCloud</title>
<style>
  body { margin:0; padding:0; background:#f4f6f9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
  .wrap { max-width:560px; margin:32px auto; background:#fff; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
  .header { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#198754,#20c997); padding:40px 32px; text-align:center; color:#fff; }
  .header h1 { margin:0 0 6px; font-size:26px; }
  .header p { margin:0; opacity:.9; font-size:15px; }
  .body { padding:32px; }
  .body h2 { color:#198754; margin-top:0; }
  .feature { display:flex; gap:12px; margin-bottom:14px; align-items:flex-start; }
  .feature-icon { font-size:1.4rem; min-width:28px; }
  .feature-text { font-size:14px; color:#555; }
  .btn { display:inline-block; background:#198754; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; padding:12px 28px; border-radius:8px; font-weight:bold; margin-top:20px; }
  .footer { background:#f8f9fa; padding:16px 32px; text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:#aaa; border-top:1px solid #e9ecef; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🌿 Welcome to AgriCloud!</h1>
    <p>Your agricultural community is waiting</p>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <h2>Hi {{ user.name }},</h2>
    <p style="color:#555;font-size:15px">Your account has been created successfully. Here's what you can do on AgriCloud:</p>

    <div class="feature"><div class="feature-icon">🏡</div><div class="feature-text"><strong>Manage your farms & fields</strong> — Register your farm, add fields, and track your agricultural activity.</div></div>
    <div class="feature"><div class="feature-icon">🛒</div><div class="feature-text"><strong>Marketplace</strong> — Buy and sell fresh agricultural products directly from farmers.</div></div>
    <div class="feature"><div class="feature-icon">📅</div><div class="feature-text"><strong>Events</strong> — Discover and join farming workshops, conferences, and community events.</div></div>
    <div class="feature"><div class="feature-icon">📝</div><div class="feature-text"><strong>Blog</strong> — Read and share knowledge about agriculture, sustainability, and best practices.</div></div>

    <center><a href="{{ login_url }}" class="btn">Go to AgriCloud →</a></center>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    © {{ "now"|date("Y") }} AgriCloud · You received this email because you created an account.
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
